asterline-rules

This package implements rule/context loading for Asterline plugins.
Its behavior is ported from pi-rules in the pi coding-agent extension ecosystem
and inspired by Asterline (asterline) at https://github.com/code-yeongyu/Asterline,
including asterline's `.asterline/rules/` workflow and rules-injector hook architecture.
